for%20a%20person%20to%20set%20foot%20on%20Indian%20Creek%20without%20the%20express%20permission%20of%20one%20of%20its%2089%20residents%20or%20a%20member%20of%20its%20ultra%20exclusive%20country%20club%2C%20which%20reportedly%20costs%20%24500%2C000%20to%20join.%20Because%20the%20town's%20government%20serves%20such%20an%20ultra%20wealthy%20subset%20of%20the%20population%2C%20things%20like%20public%20parks%20and%20social%20programs%20are%20practically%20nonexistent.%20Instead%2C%20the%20lion's%20share%20of%20Indian%20Creek's%20budget%20goes%20to%20its%20police%20department%20%E2%80%94%20which%20keeps%20watch%20on%20the%20island's%20sole%20entrance%20and%20patrols%20the%20perimeter%2024%2F7.%20Through%20federal%20funds%2C%20the%20town%20has%20also%20amassed%20a%20panoply%20of%20other%20security%20measures%20that%20would%20make%20Bezos'%20Ring%20cameras%20blush.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20wealthier%20you%20become%2C%20the%20more%20you%20want%20perfect%20security%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Setha%20Low%2C%20the%20director%20of%20the%20Public%20Space%20Research%20Group%2C%20a%20center%20at%20the%20City%20University%20of%20New%20York%20that%20focuses%20on%20the%20access%20and%20control%20of%20everything%20from%20city%20parks%20to%20gated%20communities.%20%26quot%3BAnd%20that%20produces%20an%20industry%20making%20a%20lot%20of%20money%20off%20of%20people's%20fear.%26quot%3B%20Much%20like%20the%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fus-spy-plane-flies-taiwan-strait-after-german-warships-sailed-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Emilitary-industrial%20complex%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20she%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Bthere's%20a%20security-industrial%20complex%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3E%E2%80%94%20this%20entire%20sector%20of%20our%20economy%20being%20fed%20by%20people%20wanting%20this%20kind%20of%20security.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EI'm%20relieved%20when%20we%20pull%20away%20before%20running%20into%20an%20Indian%20Creek%20police%20patrol.%20But%20there's%20no%20doubt%20we've%20been%20seen.%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3EIn%20an%20increasingly%20atomized%20age%2C%20the%20Billionaire%20Bunker%20is%20an%20increasingly%20insular%20and%20secure%20enclave.%20If%20you%20want%20to%20live%20in%20a%20part%20of%20America%20that%20no%20outsiders%20can%20set%20foot%20in%2C%20Indian%20Creek%20is%20the%20most%20gated%20community%20in%20a%20country%20of%20gates.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EDredged%20from%20the%20Tiffany-blue%20waters%20of%20Biscayne%20Bay%3Cstrong%3E%20%3C%2Fstrong%3Ein%201928%2C%20Indian%20Creek%20was%20incorporated%20in%201939%20under%20a%20now%20defunct%20Florida%20law%20that%20allowed%20groups%20of%20more%20than%2025%20people%20to%20form%20their%20own%20municipalities.%20Designed%20to%20re-create%20the%20English%20countryside%2C%20the%20300-acre%20island%20is%20more%20than%2080%25%20golf%20course%2C%20encircled%20by%20a%20single%20road%20and%2030%20or%20so%20mansions.%20The%20village%20was%20initially%20envisioned%20as%20a%20refuge%20for%20wealthy%20white%20gentiles.%20Early%20residents%20included%20William%20Henry%20Hoover%2C%20of%20vacuum%20fame%2C%20and%20Frank%20Woolworth%2C%20the%20eponymous%20founder%20of%20the%20department-store%20chain.%20Back%20then%2C%20residents%20conspired%20to%20keep%20Jewish%20homebuyers%20out%20by%20running%20their%20electric%20services%20exclusively%20through%20the%20formally%20segregated%20Indian%20Creek%20Country%20Club.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22boats%20surrounding%20an%20island%20at%20night%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e9948ece3009a0fac6c915%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EAn%20Israeli-designed%20radar%20system%20encircling%20the%20island%20can%20detect%20passersby%2C%20in%20low%20visibility%2C%20from%20half%20a%20mile%20away.%3Cp%3ESaratta%20Chuengsatiansup%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20system%20of%20de%20facto%20segregation%20no%20longer%20exists%2C%20but%20Indian%20Creek%20remains%20fixated%20on%20keeping%20certain%20people%20out.%20%26quot%3BThe%20security%20is%20very%20different%20than%20how%20it%20used%20to%20be%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Gerardo%20Vildostegui%2C%20who%20grew%20up%20in%20the%20neighboring%20town%20of%20Surfside%2C%20a%20middle-class%20community%20that%20shares%20a%20two-lane%20bridge%20with%20Indian%20Creek.%20A%20member%20of%20Surfside's%20town%20council%2C%20Vildostegui%20recalls%20a%20time%20in%20the%20early%20'90s%20when%20he%20could%20bring%20his%20college%20friends%20to%20Indian%20Creek's%20gate%20and%20get%20permission%20from%20the%20police%20to%20give%20them%20a%20tour%20of%20the%20island.%20Now%20if%20he%20approaches%20the%20bridge%2C%20the%20cops%20start%20flashing%20their%20lights%20and%20order%20him%20to%20back%20away.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20the%201980s%2C%20the%20island's%20police%20force%20%E2%80%94%20whose%20motto%20is%20%26quot%3Bprotecting%20and%20serving%20America's%20most%20exclusive%20municipality%26quot%3B%20%E2%80%94%20was%20made%20up%20of%2011%20people.%20Recent%20town%20documents%20show%20they%20employ%2019%2C%20one%20for%20every%20five%20residents.%20That's%20compared%20with%20a%20national%20average%20of%20about%202.4%20cops%20per%201%2C000%20residents.%20If%20New%20York%20City%20had%20the%20same%20officer-to-citizen%20ratio%20as%20Indian%20Creek%2C%20it%20would%20employ%20more%20than%201.5%20million%20cops.%20Because%20Indian%20Creek's%20denizens%20are%20jet-setting%20billionaires%20with%20homes%20all%20over%20the%20world%2C%20there%20are%20likely%20many%20days%20of%20the%20year%20when%20police%20officers%20actually%20outnumber%20the%20island's%20residents.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EOften%20described%20as%20%26quot%3Bbutlers%20with%20badges%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20Indian%20Creek%20police%20force%20is%20unlike%20most%20of%20its%20counterparts.%20For%20starters%2C%20it's%20nonunion.%20The%20town%20government%20quashed%20a%20union%20drive%20in%20the%201980s%2C%20firing%20a%20lead%20organizer%20accused%20of%20taking%20gasoline%20from%20a%20town%20tank.%20And%20rather%20than%20responding%20to%20calls%20from%20citizens%20in%20need%2C%20the%20police%20spend%20an%20estimated%2097%25%20of%20their%20time%20on%20security%20work%2C%20like%20patrolling%20the%20island's%20perimeter%20in%20three%20high-speed%20police%20boats%20and%20manning%20the%20access%20command%20center%20by%20the%20bridge.%20The%20force's%20recruitment%20materials%20say%20officers%20have%20%26quot%3Bextremely%20high%20levels%20of%20training%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20weapons%2C%20defensive%20tactics%2C%20and%20tactical%20operations%26quot%3B%20and%20are%20trained%20to%20use%20fully%20automatic%20firearms.%20All%20told%2C%20the%20town%20spent%20%244.1%20million%20%E2%80%94%20a%20whopping%2074%25%20of%20its%20budget%20%E2%80%94%20on%20public%20safety%20in%20fiscal%20year%202023.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%202011%2C%20the%20town%20installed%20new%20cameras%20by%20the%20entrance%20gate%20that%20allow%20police%20to%20simultaneously%20view%20a%20visitor's%20face%2C%20pull%20up%20their%20driver's%20license%2C%20and%20read%20their%20license%20plate.%20Indian%20Creek%20also%20narrowed%20the%20gate's%20opening%20to%20create%20what%20it%20called%20%26quot%3Ba%20greater%20sense%20of%20exclusivity.%26quot%3B%20In%202012%20the%20town%20replaced%20the%20tinted%20bullet-resistant%20glass%20in%20the%20access%20command%20center%2C%20and%20in%202013%20it%20added%20a%20fence%20to%20keep%20pedestrians%20out.%20Such%20investments%20are%20generally%20lauded%20by%20residents%2C%20who%20often%20push%20the%20town%20council%20for%20more%20stringent%20security%20measures.%20%26quot%3BSafety%20is%20our%20No.%201%2C%26quot%3B%20Irma%20Braman%2C%20Norman's%20wife%2C%20said%20at%20one%20meeting.%20%26quot%3BIt%20should%20be%20everyone's%20No.%201.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EWhatever%20crimes%20the%20island's%20residents%20may%20be%20committing%2C%20they%20aren't%20doing%20it%20on%20the%20island.%20Many%20years%2C%20not%20a%20single%20offense%20is%20reported%20to%20the%20Indian%20Creek%20police.%20Instead%2C%20the%20cops%20have%20their%20hands%20full%20fending%20off%20the%20curious%20boaters%20who%20try%20to%20land%20on%20the%20beach%20near%20the%20golf%20course.%20%26quot%3BThe%20police%20are%20being%20run%20ragged%20right%20now%2C%26quot%3B%20Mayor%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fjeff-bezo-79-million-mansion-indian-creek-lawsuit-leo-kryss-2024-9%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EBernard%20Klepach%3C%2Fa%3E%20%E2%80%94%20who%20is%20also%20the%20CEO%20of%20the%20world's%20largest%20in-flight%20duty-free%20company%20%E2%80%94%20said%20at%20a%20council%20meeting%20in%202020%2C%20referring%20not%20to%20a%20crime%20wave%20but%20to%20recent%20incursions%20by%20beachgoers.%20%26quot%3BWe%20need%20something%20quickly.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThat%20year%2C%20Indian%20Creek%20began%20its%20most%20substantial%20security%20upgrade%20in%20decades%20%E2%80%94%20a%20high-tech%20radar%20fence%20encircling%20the%20island.%20According%20to%20public%20records%2C%20the%20system%20features%2010%20thermal%20cameras%20and%2017%20radar%20sensors%20mounted%20at%20nine%20locations%20along%20the%20island's%20perimeter%2C%20in%20addition%20to%2030%20traditional%20cameras.%20The%20radar%20sensors%20overlap%2C%20creating%20what%20the%20records%20call%20a%20%26quot%3Bgeofence%26quot%3B%20that%20can%20detect%20anything%20that%20comes%20within%20a%20half-mile%20of%20the%20shore.%20The%20project%20cost%20about%20%241.6%20million%20%E2%80%94%20equal%20to%20about%20a%20quarter%20of%20the%20village's%20annual%20budget.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20radars%20were%20built%20by%20Magos%2C%20an%20Israeli%20company%20whose%20founders%20worked%20with%20military%20radar%20technology%20before%20shifting%20their%20focus%20to%20private%20security.%20Its%20website%20says%20Magos%20radar%20systems%20are%20generally%20used%20in%20data%20centers%2C%20oil%20and%20gas%20facilities%2C%20and%20solar%20farms.%20%26quot%3BRadar%20works%20extremely%20well%20in%20wide-open%20spaces%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Mike%20Bullman%2C%20who%20runs%20Safe%20Security%20Solutions%2C%20a%20perimeter-security%20company%20that%20has%20installed%20Magos%20radars%20around%20large%20country%20estates%20in%20the%20United%20Kingdom.%20But%20he%20and%20several%20other%20security%20professionals%20I%20spoke%20with%20had%20never%20heard%20of%20one%20being%20installed%20around%20an%20entire%20town.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20Indian%20Creek%20radar%20can%20detect%20objects%20on%20the%20water%20and%20use%20artificial%20intelligence%20to%20classify%20them%20according%20to%20the%20risk%20they%20pose.%20When%20a%20potential%20threat%20is%20detected%2C%20the%20system%20automatically%20moves%20a%20thermal%20camera%20to%20track%20it.%20Police%20officers%20at%20the%20station%20can%20watch%20a%20live%20feed%20on%20a%20software%20called%20%26quot%3BOctopus%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20dispatch%20a%20patrol%20boat%20to%20investigate.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%223900%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22An%20aerial%20view%20of%20Indian%20Creek%20Island.%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F64d5daaa005c4a00183db886%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222600%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIn%202014%2C%20the%20estimated%20net%20worth%20of%20the%20island's%2086%20residents%20was%20%2437%20billion.%20Bezos%20added%20%24199%20billion.%3Cp%3EChandan%20Khanna%2FAFP%20via%20Getty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EJustin%20Ross%2C%20who's%20been%20running%20tours%20of%20the%20Biscayne%20Bay%20for%20several%20years%2C%20first%20noticed%20the%20perimeter-security%20system%20while%20boating%20past%20the%20island%20one%20evening%20in%202022.%20A%20red%20light%20from%20the%20shore%20appeared%20to%20latch%20on%20to%20his%20boat.%20%26quot%3BI%20could%20see%20it%20moving%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20recalls.%20%26quot%3BI%20was%20like%2C%20oh%20wow%2C%20it's%20following%20me.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWith%20the%20new%20security%20system%2C%20the%20Indian%20Creek%20police%20appear%20to%20have%20turbocharged%20their%20enforcement%20of%20regulations%20in%20the%20surrounding%20waters.%20In%202019%2C%20the%20department%20issued%20211%20traffic%20and%20marine%20citations.%20In%202022%2C%20the%20first%20year%20the%20radar%20system%20was%20fully%20operational%2C%20the%20number%20of%20citations%20soared%20to%201%2C600.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BEvery%20time%20I%20go%20past%20Indian%20Creek%2C%20I%20run%20into%20a%20marine%20patrol%20guy%2C%26quot%3B%20Ross%20says.%20He%20knows%20of%20plenty%20of%20boaters%20who%20have%20been%20ticketed%2C%20generally%20for%20creating%20a%20wake%20too%20close%20to%20the%20shore.%20Passing%20by%20the%20island%20earlier%20this%20year%2C%20%3Cspan%3ERoss%20triggered%20the%20attention%20of%20an%20Indian%20Creek%20Police%20patrol.%3C%2Fspan%3E%20The%20officer%20hit%20him%20with%20a%20%24140%20ticket%20for%20not%20having%20the%20correct%20safety%20equipment%20on%20board.%20The%20Indian%20Creek%20police%20department%20did%20not%20respond%20to%20my%20inquiries.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EResidents%2C%20for%20their%20part%2C%20have%20been%20enthusiastic%20about%20the%20new%20system%2C%20and%20several%20granted%20easements%20to%20allow%20the%20tech%20to%20be%20mounted%20on%20their%20property.%20One%20key%20selling%20point%20for%20the%20ultra%20wealthy%20townies%3A%20The%20cameras%20would%20never%20be%20pointed%20inward.%20Only%20outsiders%20would%20be%20targeted%20by%20the%20high-tech%20system.%20%26quot%3BI%20think%20the%20security%20is%20great%20and%20have%20been%20happy%20with%20what%20has%20been%20implemented%2C%26quot%3B%20Gail%20Golden%2C%20the%20wife%20of%20Carl%20Icahn%2C%20tells%20me.%20%26quot%3BNothing%20further%20to%20add.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20August%202023%2C%20about%20a%20year%20after%20the%20perimeter%20system%20was%20installed%2C%20Indian%20Creek%20residents%20learned%20that%20they%20had%20a%20new%20neighbor.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fphotos-indian-creek-billionaire-bunker-miami-private-island-tour-2022-12%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3EJeff%20Bezos%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20world's%20second-richest%20man%2C%20had%20spent%20%2468%20million%20on%20a%20waterfront%20mansion%2C%20quickly%20followed%20by%20the%20purchase%20of%20an%20abutting%20property%20worth%20%2479%20million.%20Then%2C%20last%20April%2C%20he%20completed%20a%20billionaire's%20hat%20trick%2C%20grabbing%20a%20%2490%20million%20mansion%20from%20Javier%20Holtz%2C%20the%20retired%20chairman%20and%20CEO%20of%20Marquis%20Bank.%20The%20Amazon%20tycoon%20got%20to%20work%2C%20applying%20to%20build%20a%20pickleball%20court%20in%20one%20of%20his%20yards%20and%20making%20plans%20to%20tear%20down%20two%20of%20the%20dwellings%20to%20construct%20one%20supermansion.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EBezos'%20arrival%20catapulted%20the%20wealth%20of%20Indian%20Creek%20into%20a%20new%20stratosphere.%20In%202014%2C%20the%20entire%20net%20worth%20of%20the%20island's%2086%20residents%20was%20estimated%20at%20%2437%20billion.%20Bezos%20added%20%24199%20billion.%20The%20total%20value%20of%20property%20on%20the%20island%20is%20approaching%20%241%20billion%20and%20seems%20poised%20to%20climb.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPeople's%20price%20expectations%20just%20jumped%20drastically%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Marko%20Gojanovic%2C%20a%20real-estate%20agent%20who%20has%20shown%20several%20houses%20on%20the%20island.%20Prices%20have%20more%20than%20doubled%20since%20the%20start%20of%20the%20pandemic%20and%20have%20increased%20by%20at%20least%20another%2020%25%20since%20the%20first%20Bezos%20deal.%20Gojanovic%20says%20he's%20been%20asking%20as%20much%20as%20%24150%20million%20for%20certain%20properties.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20real-estate%20agents%2C%20Gojanovic%20says%2C%20%26quot%3Baccess%20to%20Indian%20Creek%20is%20almost%20like%20gold.%26quot%3B%20In%20off-market%20transactions%20like%20the%20Bezos%20sales%2C%20two%20or%20three%20brokers%20can%20find%20themselves%20pitching%20the%20same%20property.%20Agents%20are%20expected%20to%20keep%20transactions%20private%2C%20and%20Gojanovic%20says%20nondisclosure%20agreements%20are%20common.%20The%20true%20owners%20of%20several%20Indian%20Creek%20properties%20remain%20undisclosed%2C%20including%20the%20buyer%20of%20a%20%2465%20million%20property%20purchased%20this%20May.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EDina%20Goldentayer%2C%20who%20served%20as%20the%20broker%20for%20one%20of%20the%20Bezos%20properties%2C%20says%20security%20has%20become%20a%20major%20selling%20point%20for%20prospective%20buyers.%20%26quot%3BThese%20people%20are%20buying%20a%20secure%20lifestyle%20as%20much%20as%20they're%20buying%20a%20big%20house%2C%26quot%3B%20she%20says.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIn%20recent%20years%2C%20the%20island%2C%20which%20has%20long%20served%20as%20a%20haven%20for%20the%20elite%2C%20has%20become%20even%20more%20exclusive.%20Vildostegui%2C%20the%20Surfside%20town%20council%20member%2C%20says%20Island%20Creek%20residents%20used%20to%20feel%20more%20like%20local%20celebrities%20%E2%80%94%20guys%20like%20Don%20Shula%2C%20the%20coach%20of%20the%20Miami%20Dolphins%2C%20who%20you%20might%20run%20into%20at%20church.%20Now%2C%20Vildostegui%20says%2C%20the%20island%20has%20become%20%26quot%3Ba%20spot%20on%20the%20international%20billionaire%20circuit.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20new%20arrivals%20have%20triggered%20a%20bit%20of%20a%20building%20boom%2C%20with%20several%20projects%20now%20under%20construction.%20When%20I%20visit%20the%20entrance%20on%20a%20Tuesday%20afternoon%2C%20I%20count%20about%2030%20vehicles%20entering%20and%20exiting%20in%20less%20than%2010%20minutes%20%E2%80%94%20the%20Teslas%20and%20BMWs%20of%20the%20residents%20and%20country-club%20members%20mixed%20in%20with%20the%20pickups%2C%20vans%2C%20and%20Toyotas%20of%20construction%20workers.%20A%20sign%20by%20the%20entrance%20gate%20reads%20%26quot%3BNo%20Trespassing%3A%20Private%20Island%2C%26quot%3B%20and%20a%20black%20police%20SUV%20idles%20nearby.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%222000%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Trucks%20driving%20towards%20a%20locked%20safe%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e994b5d17aa3c7b2b34e4f%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%221500%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EIndian%20Creek%20reflects%20the%20growing%20rise%20of%20the%20security-industrial%20complex%2C%20a%20burgeoning%20field%20aimed%20at%20assuaging%20the%20anxieties%20of%20the%20superwealthy.%3Cp%3ESaratta%20Chuengsatiansup%20for%20BI%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cp%3EDespite%20the%20Billionaire%20Bunker's%20fixation%20on%20remaining%20insular%2C%20it%20tends%20to%20encroach%20on%20the%20outside%20world.%20With%20on-island%20parking%20limited%20to%20construction%20supervisors%2C%20crews%20working%20on%20Indian%20Creek%20mansions%20sometimes%20park%20along%20a%20quiet%20Surfside%20street%20near%20the%20bridge.%20Properties%20in%20the%20neighborhood%20are%20also%20being%20bought%20up%20by%20opaquely%20named%20LLCs%20tied%20to%20Indian%20Creek%20residents.%20Julio%20Iglesias%2C%20a%20longtime%20Indian%20Creek%20homeowner%2C%20is%20particularly%20invested%20in%20Surfside%2C%20controlling%20through%20several%20LLCs%20at%20least%20nine%20properties%20within%20a%20few%20blocks%20of%20the%20entrance.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20sprawl%20into%20Surfside%20became%20a%20flashpoint%20in%20the%20late%201990s%2C%20when%20Indian%20Creek%20began%20building%20a%20new%20police%20and%20government%20complex%20on%20the%20other%20side%20of%20the%20bridge.%20Some%20Surfsiders%20felt%20the%20station%20would%20change%20the%20character%20of%20their%20neighborhood%2C%20and%20the%20conflict%20grew%20petty%2C%20bringing%20long-simmering%20class%20tension%20to%20the%20surface.%20Town%20officials%20snubbed%20each%20other%20at%20community%20meetings%20and%20filed%20competing%20lawsuits.%20%26quot%3BWe%20used%20to%20tease%20each%20other%20that%2C%20for%20them%2C%20Surfside%20was%20spelled%20with%20an%20E%20instead%20of%20a%20U%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Tim%20Will%2C%20who%20served%20as%20a%20Surfside%20commissioner%20during%20the%20spat.%20%26quot%3BThey%20don't%20interact%20with%20us%20unless%20you're%20cutting%20their%20lawns%20or%20building%20their%20piers.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EWill%20was%20particularly%20bothered%20by%20the%20bridge%20connecting%20the%20two%20towns%2C%20which%20receives%20public%20money%20for%20repair%20projects%20but%20which%20the%20public%20is%20forbidden%20from%20crossing.%20Actually%2C%20Indian%20Creek%20often%20makes%20use%20of%20public%20funds%20to%20maintain%20its%20privacy%20%E2%80%94%20security%20projects%20like%20the%20radar%20system%20are%20almost%20always%20funded%20via%20a%20federal%20forfeiture%20fund.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EIndian%20Creek%20eventually%20won%20the%20turf%20war%2C%20and%20the%20new%20police%20station%20was%20built.%20Tensions%20with%20Surfside%20seem%20to%20have%20cooled%2C%20but%20the%20questions%20of%20public%20funding%20and%20public%20access%20remain.%20The%20bridge%20received%20%24875%2C000%20in%20government%20grants%20in%202008%2C%20and%20last%20November%20the%20town%20requested%20another%20%24400%2C000%20for%20repairs.%20But%20when%20I%20visit%20the%20police%20station%20at%20the%20bridge%20and%20ask%20if%20I%20can%20walk%20across%2C%20I'm%20barred%20from%20entering.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3EIndian%20Creek's%20growing%20wealth%20and%20security%20mirror%20trends%20among%20the%20global%20superrich.%20Over%20the%20past%20four%20years%2C%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Finequality.org%2Fgreat-divide%2Fbillionaire-wealth-up-88-percent-over-four-years%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3E%3Cu%3Ebillionaire%20wealth%20has%20grown%20by%2088%25%3C%2Fu%3E%3C%2Fa%3E.%20In%20April%2C%20America's%20806%20billionaires%20boasted%20a%20net%20worth%20of%20%245.8%20trillion%2C%20greater%20than%20the%20annual%20GDPs%20of%20Japan%2C%20Germany%2C%20and%20India%20%E2%80%94%20and%20more%20wealth%20than%20the%20bottom%20half%20of%20America.%20Miami%20is%20frequently%20said%20to%20be%20the%20US%20city%20with%20the%20most%20extreme%20income%20inequality.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EThe%20growing%20wealth%20gap%20has%20given%20rise%20to%20the%20security-industrial%20complex%2C%20a%20burgeoning%20field%20aimed%20at%20assuaging%20the%20anxieties%20of%20the%20superwealthy.%20Multiple%20billionaire-security%20professionals%20I%20spoke%20with%20described%20an%20increased%20interest%20in%20security%20among%20their%20ultra-high-net-worth%20clients.%20Some%20are%20shelling%20out%20millions%20on%20highly%20trained%20bodyguards%20or%20deploying%20high-tech%20surveillance%20drones.%20Elon%20Musk%20travels%20with%20up%20to%2020%20bodyguards%20at%20a%20time.%20Others%20are%20building%20bunkers%20to%20wait%20out%20the%20apocalypse.%20In%20Indian%20Creek%2C%20if%20you%20somehow%20evaded%20the%20islandwide%20surveillance%20dragnet%20that%20Bezos%20and%20his%20neighbors%20have%20amassed%20through%20public%20funding%2C%20you'd%20still%20have%20to%20contend%20with%20the%20formidable%20private%20dragnets%20guarding%20their%20individual%20mansions.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3ESecurity%20%26quot%3Bhas%20become%20a%20really%20big%20concern%20for%20billionaires%20now%2C%20because%20there's%20never%20been%20more%20talk%20about%20the%20divide%20between%20the%20haves%20and%20the%20have-nots%2C%26quot%3B%20says%20Brian%20Daniel%2C%20who%20operates%20the%20Celebrity%20Personal%20Assistant%20Network%2C%20a%20company%20that%20connects%20billionaires%20to%20security%20staff.%20%26quot%3BIt%20gets%20people%20worked%20up.%26quot%3B%20Never%20mind%20that%20poor%20people%20are%20statistically%20far%20more%20likely%20to%20be%20the%20victims%20of%20crime%20than%20those%20who%20can%20afford%20supermansions%20on%20private%20islands.%20Being%20rich%20means%20you%20can%20afford%20to%20be%20safe%20instead%20of%20sorry.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BTrapped%2C%26quot%3B%20a%20book%20coauthored%20by%3Cem%3E%20%3C%2Fem%3ELow%2C%20the%20CUNY%20researcher%2C%20describes%20a%20growing%20movement%20to%20build%20communities%20that%20are%20%26quot%3Bprivatized%2C%20fortified%2C%20unequal.%26quot%3B%20By%202015%2C%20more%20than%2011%20million%20Americans%20had%20retreated%20to%20these%20%26quot%3Bsecured%20communities%2C%26quot%3B%20compared%20with%207%20million%20a%20decade%20earlier.%20But%20rather%20than%20making%20residents%20feel%20safer%2C%20Low%20says%2C%20the%20intense%20focus%20on%20security%20and%20privacy%20only%20serves%20to%20cut%20them%20off%20from%20the%20public%20and%20stoke%20their%20anxieties%20about%20outsiders.%20Walled-off%20communities%2C%20by%20their%20very%20nature%2C%20lead%20to%20ever%20higher%20walls.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndian%20Creek%20is%20a%20great%20extreme%20example%20of%20trying%20to%20pull%20out%20completely%20from%20having%20anything%20to%20do%20with%20the%20rest%20of%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20Low%20says.%20%26quot%3BThe%20more%20you%20enclose%20yourself%2C%20the%20more%20you're%20reminding%20yourself%20of%20a%20sense%20of%20risk.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EAt%20a%20council%20meeting%20in%202022%2C%20not%20long%20after%20the%20installation%20of%20the%20perimeter-security%20system%2C%20Indian%20Creek%20residents%20were%20once%20again%20discussing%20the%20need%20to%20ramp%20up%20their%20security.%20This%20time%2C%20they%20worried%20the%20threat%20might%20be%20coming%20from%20%3Cem%3Einside%20%3C%2Fem%3Ethe%20mansions.%20The%20police%20chief%2C%20John%20Bernardo%2C%20proposed%20a%20measure%20that%20would%20require%20any%20worker%20entering%20the%20island%20to%20submit%20to%20a%20criminal%20background%20check.%20Despite%20pushback%20from%20some%20residents%20who%20were%20concerned%20that%20the%20policy%20would%20make%20hiring%20more%20difficult%2C%20the%20council%20came%20down%20largely%20in%20support%20of%20the%20idea.%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cp%3EFor%20Mayor%20Klepach%2C%20the%20background%20checks%20were%20just%20a%20starting%20point.%20More%20wealth%20leads%20to%20more%20workers%20%E2%80%94%20and%20every%20worker%20is%20a%20potential%20threat.%26quot%3BEspecially%20when%20you%20have%20so%20many%20houses%20going%20up%20and%20a%20caravan%20of%20employees%20coming%20in%20and%20out%20of%20here%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mayor%20said%2C%20%26quot%3Bwe%20could%20do%20so%20much%20more.%26quot%3B%3C%2Fp%3E%3Chr%3E%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3EGuthrie%20Scrimgeour%20is%20an%20investigative%20journalist%20based%20in%20Washington%2C%20DC%2C%20covering%20wealth%20and%20power.%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%3Cdiv%3ERead%20the%20original%20article%20on%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-bunker-miami-bezos-tom-brady-ivanka-trump-security-2024-9%5C%22%3EBusiness%20Insider%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726998902000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66e994e3d17aa3c7b2b34e8d%3Fformat%3Djpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-bunker-miami-bezos-tom-brady-ivanka-trump-security-2024-9%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22It's%20America's%20wealthiest%20town.%20Approach%20at%20your%20own%20peril.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22insider%40insider.com%20(Guthrie%20Scrimgeour)%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.businessinsider.com%2Fbillionaire-bunker-miami-bezos-tom-brady-ivanka-trump-security-2024-9%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22The%20self-driving%20future%20will%20look%20unremarkable.%20That's%20the%20point.%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20width%3D%5C%224471%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22Waymo%20are%5C%22%20charset%3D%5C%22%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fi.insider.com%2F66ef720bcfb7f307e573c272%3Fformat%3Djpeg%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%222236%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%3EWaymo's%20robot%20taxis%20have%20become%20a%20ubiquitous%20fixture%20in%20the%20city%20of%20San%20Francisco.%3Cp%3EMario%20Tama%2FGetty%20Images%3C%2Fp%3E%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3Cul%3E%3Cli%3EWaymo's%20robot%20taxis%20debuted%