handran%20Ashwin%3C%2Fa%3E%20has%20insisted%20that%20people%20have%20doubted%20his%20credentials%20a%20Test%20cricketer%20for%20India%20throughout%20his%20career%2C%20mainly%20because%20he%20made%20his%20name%20as%20a%20bowler%20in%20the%20Indian%20Premier%20League%20(IPL).%20Ashwin%20added%20that%20he%20came%20into%20the%20Indian%20Test%20set%20up%20as%20a%20replacement%20of%20former%20off-spinner%20Harbhajan%20Singh%2C%20but%20admitted%20that%20people%20doubted%20whether%20he%20could%20actually%20fill%20in%20such%20big%20shoes.%20However%2C%20with%20101%20Tests%20and%20522%20wickets%20in%20the%20bag%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20managed%20to%20win%20over%20his%20doubters.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%2038-year-old%20took%20seven%20wickets%20and%20scored%20a%20crucial%20century%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20to%20help%20India%20beat%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Sunday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20already%20has%20more%20wickets%20that%20Harbhajan%2C%20who%20was%20his%20idol%20growing%20up.%20With%2037%20Test%20five-fors%20to%20his%20name%2C%20Ashwin%20has%20surely%20cemented%20his%20place%20in%20the%20history%20of%20Test%20cricket.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20can't%20really%20comment%20on%20what%20sort%20of%20impact%20I%20have%20had%20on%20this%20Test%20match.%20I%20had%20huge%20shoes%20to%20fill%2C%20I%20came%20in%20to%20replace%20Harbhajan%2C%20I%20used%20to%20replicate%20his%20action%20in%20junior%20cricket%2C%20he%20was%20an%20inspiration%20to%20me.%20Constantly%20people%20have%20doubted%20if%20I%20could%20deliver%20in%20red-ball%20as%20I%20came%20from%20IPL%2C%20lots%20of%20people%20have%20come%20and%20helped%20me%2C%26quot%3B%20Ashwin%20said%20after%20the%20match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAshwin%20added%20he%20approaches%20the%20game%20with%20a%20bowler's%20mindset%20and%20batting%20comes%20to%20him%20naturally%2C%20adding%20that%20he%20is%20learning%20to%20compartmentalise%20the%20two%20aspects%20of%20the%20game.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20make%20a%20living%20by%20bowling%2C%20so%20bowling%20comes%20first.%20Batting%20is%20something%20that%20comes%20naturally%20but%20I%20have%20focused%20my%20thoughts%20with%20batting.%20Over%20the%20last%20few%20years.%20I%20have%20tried%20to%20compartmentalise.%20It%20is%20a%20work%20in%20progress%2C%26quot%3B%20he%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BI%20am%20probably%20enjoying%20my%20play%20because%20of%20what%20I%20am%20doing%20not%20because%20of%20what%20I%20want%20to%20get%20out%20of%20it.%26quot%3B%20%26quot%3BIt%20(the%20century)%20was%20an%20opportunity%20to%20fight%2C%20dig%20in%20deep.%20I've%20seen%20so%20many%20teammates%20do%20it%20in%20the%20past.%20It%20was%20a%20special%20innings%2C%20didn't%20sink%20in%20till%20day%202.%20Every%20time%20I%20play%20in%20Chennai%2C%20it's%20an%20amazing%20feeling.%20I've%20watched%20a%20lot%20of%20Tests%2C%20international%20cricket%20in%20those%20stands%2C%20to%20do%20it%20in%20front%20of%20those%20renovated%20stands%20is%20great%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20Ashwin%2C%20who%20was%20named%20Man%20of%20the%20Match.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E(With%20PTI%20Inputs)%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726995120000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fq95rpdp8_r-ashwin-bcci_625x300_22_September_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fsports.ndtv.com%2Findia-vs-bangladesh-2024%2Fconstantly-people-have-doubted-ravichandran-ashwin-on-replacing-harbhajan-singh-in-indian-team-6622824%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22R%20Ashwin%20took%20seven%20wickets%20and%20scored%20a%20crucial%20century%20in%20the%20first%20innings%20to%20help%20India%20beat%20Bangladesh%20in%20the%20first%20Test%20in%20Chennai%20on%20Sunday.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22KJo%20teases%20Vedang%20Raina%20with%20Khushi's%20name%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726995107000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fs