com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-san-francisco-officer-dresses-in-bright-chicken-costume-to-promote-traffic-safety%2Farticleshow%2F113567324.cms%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-san-francisco-officer-dresses-in-bright-chicken-costume-to-promote-traffic-safety%2Famp_articleshow%2F113567324.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Fwatch-san-francisco-officer-dresses-in-bright-chicken-costume-to-promote-traffic-safety%2Famp_articleshow%2F113567324.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Opinion%3A%20Quad%20-%20And%20India's%20Role%20In%20It%20-%20Will%20Remain%20Relevant%2C%20Thanks%20To%20China%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%3E%3Cimg%20alt%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20title%3D%5C%22Latest%20and%20Breaking%20News%20on%20NDTV%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fsoo946v_quad-summit_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%5C%22%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20idea%20of%20the%20Quad%20is%20now%20almost%20two%20decades%20old%2C%20emerging%20for%20the%20first%20time%20after%20the%20tsunami%20in%202004.%20Yet%2C%20a%20tone%20of%20tentativeness%20seems%20to%20surround%20this%20diplomatic%20partnership%2C%20often%20reflected%20in%20experts%20and%20media%20questioning%20its%20worth%2C%20need%2C%20or%20even%20existence.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20fourth%20Quad%20leaders'%20summit%20in%20Wilmington%2C%20Delaware%2C%20was%20no%20different.%20Ahead%20of%20the%20summit's%20start%2C%20a%20reporter%20asked%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20if%20the%20Quad%20would%20exist%20beyond%20November.%20He%20quipped%2C%20%26quot%3BMuch%20beyond%20that%26quot%3B%2C%20and%20then%20reiterated%20the%20sentiment%20in%20his%20opening%20statement%20at%20the%20summit.%20%26quot%3BChallenges%20will%20come%2C%20the%20world%20will%20change%2C%20but%20the%20Quad%20is%20here%20to%20stay.%26quot%3B%20He%20was%20backed%20by%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20of%20India%2C%20who%20added%20that%20the%20Quad%20was%20here%20to%20assist%2C%20partner%2C%20and%20complement%20the%20efforts%20of%20Indo-Pacific%20countries.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EThe%20Impact%20Of%20AUKUS%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202021%2C%20just%20a%20week%20before%20the%20first%20in-person%20Quad%20summit%20in%20Washington%2C%20D.C.%2C%20the%20U.S.%20announced%20a%20new%20trilateral%20security%20partnership%20-%20AUKUS%20-%20with%20an%20objective%20similar%20to%20that%20of%20the%20Quad%3A%20promoting%20a%20free%20and%20open%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20The%20announcement%20of%20AUKUS%2C%20with%20its%20clear%20military%20aspect%2C%20immediately%20raised%20questions%20about%20the%20Quad%2C%20a%20partnership%20without%20any%20military%20component.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20re-emergence%20of%20the%20Quad%20in%202017%2C%20after%20lying%20dormant%20for%20more%20than%20a%20decade%2C%20was%20tempered%20by%20some%20hesitation%20from%20India%20and%20Australia.%20India%2C%20a%20neighbour%20of%20China%2C%20and%20Australia%2C%20with%20its%20trade%20dependence%20on%20China%2C%20were%20wary%20of%20antagonising%20Beijing%20by%20appearing%20to%20participate%20in%20what%20Chinese%20President%20Xi%20Jinping%20called%20a%20'U.S.-led%20Western%20effort'%20to%20contain%2C%20encircle%2C%20and%20suppress%20China.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%202020%20changed%20the%20stance%20of%20both%20New%20Delhi%20and%20Canberra.%20India%20became%20locked%20in%20border%20friction%20with%20China%20in%20Eastern%20Ladakh%2C%20and%20Australia%20faced%20a%20trade%20backlash%20from%20China%20as%20it%20pushed%20for%20a%20resolution%20to%20identify%20the%20origin%20of%20COVID-19.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThat%20year%20saw%20India%20advocating%20for%20the%20second%20and%20stand-alone%20ministerial%20meeting%20of%20the%20Quad%20in%20Tokyo%2C%20despite%20the%20ongoing%20pandemic.%20The%20first%20ministerial%20meeting%20took%20place%20in%20New%20York%20on%20the%20sidelines%20of%20the%20United%20Nations%20General%20Assembly%20(UNGA).%20It%20was%20clear%20that%20inhibitions%20had%20been%20shed%20and%20the%20Quad%20was%20finally%20coming%20into%20its%20own.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EWhere%20Quad%20Has%20%3Cem%3EReally%20%3C%2Fem%3EProved%20Relevant%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHowever%2C%20since%20the%20firming%20up%20of%20AUKUS%20-%20the%20security%20partnership%20between%20Australia%2C%20the%20UK%2C%20and%20the%20U.S.%20-%20comparisons%20are%20often%20drawn%20to%20the%20Quad%20and%20its%20possible%20ineffectiveness%20in%20containing%20China%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20due%20to%20its%20lack%20of%20military%20muscle.%20Nevertheless%2C%20the%20Quad%20has%20positioned%20itself%20as%20relevant%20in%20another%20area%3A%20reducing%20China's%20influence%20in%20the%20global%20economic%20space.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20year%2C%20the%20Quad%20Summit%20announced%20the%20Supply%20Chains%20Contingency%20Network%20to%20enhance%20the%20resilience%20of%20semiconductor%20supply%20chains.%20This%20is%20a%20critical%20area%20as%20semiconductors%20play%20a%20vital%20role%20in%20today's%20world%2C%20particularly%20in%20advanced%20economies.%20A%202023%20report%20by%20the%20research%20institute%20RAND%20stated%20that%20Taiwan's%20dominance%20in%20global%20semiconductor%20production%20creates%20geopolitical%20and%20economic%20vulnerabilities%20for%20the%20US%20and%20its%20allies%2C%20as%20well%20as%20for%20Taiwan%2C%20which%20provides%20China%20with%20a%20potential%20asymmetric%20advantage.%20The%20report%20pointed%20out%20that%20a%20supply%20chain%20disruption%20could%20severely%20impact%20the%20U.S.%20economy%20and%20recommended%20that%20instead%20of%20acting%20unilaterally%2C%20Washington%20should%20engage%20its%20allies%20and%20partners%20to%20respond%20as%20a%20united%2C%20multinational%20bloc.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAnother%20example%20is%20from%202021%3A%20the%20Quad%20vaccine%20partnership.%20As%20many%20as%20400%20million%20COVID-19%20vaccine%20doses%20were%20delivered%20to%20Indo-Pacific%20countries%20to%20curtail%20China's%20vaccine%20outreach%20and%20influence%20in%20Southeast%20Asian%20nations.%20A%20consultancy%20that%20tracks%20China's%20impact%20on%20global%20health%2C%20Bridge%20Consulting%2C%20reported%20that%20China's%20vaccine%20deliveries%20in%20the%20Asia-Pacific%20category%20totalled%20890%20million%20by%20December%202022.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch2%3E%3Cstrong%3EQuad%20Is%20More%20Useful%20For%20US.%20Clue%3A%20India%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fh2%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EMoreover%2C%20while%20AUKUS%20is%20a%20completely%20global%20Western%20alliance%2C%20India's%20presence%20in%20the%20Quad%20makes%20it%20more%20useful%20for%20America.%20This%20can%20be%20better%20understood%20through%20John%20Ikenberry's%20framework%20of%20Three%20Worlds%3A%20the%20West%2C%20East%2C%20and%20South%2C%20and%20the%20competition%20to%20shape%20the%20global%20order.%20He%20states%20that%20the%20main%20axis%20of%20the%20struggle%20over%20world%20order%20runs%20between%20the%20global%20West%20and%20the%20global%20East%20(China%20and%20Russia).%20Ikenberry%20describes%20the%20global%20South%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bswing%20grouping%26quot%3B%2C%20available%20to%20join%20other%20states%20in%20ways%20that%20tilt%20world%20politics%20in%20one%20direction%20or%20the%20other.%20It%20is%20this%20role%20that%20India%20fulfils%20and%20leverages%20through%20its%20participation%20in%20the%20Quad.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EHence%2C%20both%20the%20Quad%20as%20a%20partnership%20and%20India's%20presence%20in%20such%20partnerships%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20in%20a%20world%20where%20the%20rise%20of%20China%20remains%20a%20source%20of%20fragmentation%20in%20the%20current%20liberal%20or%20American%20world%20order.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cem%3E(Maha%20Siddiqui%20is%20a%20journalist%20who%20has%20extensively%20reported%20on%20public%20policy%20and%20global%20affairs.)%3C%2Fem%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EDisclaimer%3A%20These%20are%20the%20personal%20opinions%20of%20the%20author%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726994040000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fsoo946v_quad-summit_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fopinion%2Fquad-and-indias-role-in-it-will-remain-relevant-thanks-to-china-6622898%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22Both%20the%20Quad%20as%20a%20partnership%20and%20India's%20presence%20in%20such%20partnerships%20are%20expected%20to%20continue%20in%20a%20world%20where%20the%20rise%20of%20China%20remains%20a%20source%20of%20fragmentation%20in%20the%20current%20liberal%20or%20American%20world%20order.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Detonators%2C%20Gas%20Cylinder%20Found%20On%20Rail%20Tracks%20In%20UP%2C%20Madhya%20Pradesh%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EAt%20least%2010%20detonators%20were%20found%20on%20a%20railway%20track%20in%20an%20attempt%20to%20blow%20up%20the%20train%20carrying%20Army%20personnel%20in%20Madhya%20Pradesh's%20Burhanpur%20district%2C%20officials%20said%20today.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20incident%20took%20place%20near%20the%20Sagphata%20railway%20station%20when%20the%20army's%20special%20train%20was%20travelling%20from%20Jammu%20and%20Kashmir%20to%20Karnataka%20on%20Wednesday.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EAs%20the%20train%20passed%20over%20the%20detonators%2C%20the%20driver%20became%20alert%20due%20to%20an%20explosion%20and%20promptly%20stopped%20the%20train.%20He%20then%20informed%20the%20station%20master.%20No%20one%20was%20injured%20in%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ESenior%20officials%20from%20the%20Anti-Terrorism%20Squad%20(ATS)%2C%20National%20Investigation%20Agency%20(NIA)%2C%20railways%2C%20and%20local%20police%20are%20probing%20the%20incident.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Ch3%3E%3Cstrong%3EGas%20Cylinder%20Found%20On%20Railway%20Track%20In%20UP%3C%2Fstron