op-using-upi-if-transaction-fee-levied-survey-124092200157_1.html%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Series%20Of%20Child%20Sexual%20Abuse%20Cases%20Emerge%20In%20Bhopal%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20capital%20city%20of%20Madhya%20Pradesh%20has%20witnessed%20reports%20of%20a%20series%20of%20child%20sexual%20abuse%20cases%20that%20have%20emerged%20within%20four%20days%2C%20raising%20concerns%20about%20the%20safety%20of%20children%20in%20educational%20environments.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EA%2016-year-old%20boy%20was%20allegedly%20sexually%20harassed%20by%20his%20chemistry%20teacher%20at%20a%20private%20school%20in%20Bhopal.%20The%20teacher%20reportedly%20threatened%20the%20student%20with%20failing%20grades%20and%20recorded%20inappropriate%20videos.%20The%20situation%20came%20to%20light%20when%20the%20boy's%20class%20teacher%20spoke%20to%20him%20after%20he%20received%20low%20marks%20in%20an%20examination.%20The%20school%20principal%20was%20then%20informed%2C%20leading%20to%20police%20involvement.%20An%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20the%20teacher%2C%20who%20was%20arrested%20and%20presented%20in%20court%2C%20where%20he%20was%20remanded%20to%20judicial%20custody.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20another%20incident%20on%20Saturday%2C%20a%205-year-old%20girl%20reported%20being%20sexually%20abused%20by%20her%20school%20van%20driver.%20The%20child%20returned%20home%20crying%20and%20informed%20her%20mother%20about%20the%20incident.%20But%20when%20enquired%20at%20the%20police%20station%2C%20she%20did%20not%20mention%20the%20details%20prompting%20the%20Child%20Welfare%20Committee%20(CWC)%20to%20schedule%20a%20counselling%20with%20her%20today%20to%20gather%20more%20information.%20As%20of%20now%2C%20the%20police%20have%20detained%20the%20driver%20for%20questioning%2C%20but%20no%20FIR%20has%20been%20registered%20against%20him%20yet.%20However%2C%20Bhopal%20Police%20Commissioner%20Harinarayanachari%20Mishra%20has%20confirmed%20that%20the%20case%20is%20being%20taken%20seriously.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThree%20days%20ago%2C%20a%203-year-old%20girl%20was%20sexually%20abused%20by%20her%20IT%20teacher%20at%20a%20different%20private%20school.%20Her%20mother%20noticed%20suspicious%20scratches%20on%20her%20body%2C%20which%20she%20initially%20thought%20to%20be%20accidental.%20After%20questioning%20the%20child%2C%20who%20referred%20to%20the%20perpetrator%20as%20%26quot%3Buncle%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20mother%20reported%20the%20matter%20to%20authorities.%20Following%20a%20medical%20examination%20and%20subsequent%20identification%2C%20the%20accused%20teacher%20Qasim%2C%20confessed%20to%20the%20crime%20and%20was%20arrested.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThese%20incidents%20have%20prompted%20public%20outrage%20and%20calls%20for%20immediate%20action%20to%20ensure%20child%20safety%20in%20schools.%20Chief%20Minister%20Dr%20Mohan%20Yadav%20condemned%20these%20acts%20and%20ordered%20prompt%20investigations%20into%20all%20cases.%20He%20also%20announced%20plans%20to%20establish%20a%20special%20court%20aimed%20at%20expediting%20trials%20for%20offenders.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20a%20separate%20case%20in%20Tikamgarh%2C%20a%207-year-old%20girl%20was%20allegedly%20sexually%20assaulted%20by%20Ashish%20Tiwari%2C%20a%20local%20man%20recently%20appointed%20as%20an%20MP%20representative%20by%20Union%20Minister%20Virendra%20Khatik.%20Following%20a%20complaint%20from%20the%20girl's%20mother%2C%20police%20registered%20a%20case%20under%20the%20POCSO%20Act%2C%20and%20the%20Union%20Minister%20removed%20the%20accused%20as%20his%20representative.%20However%2C%20Tiwari%20is%20currently%20absconding.%20Authorities%20are%20under%20pressure%20to%20implement%20stricter%20regulations%20and%20ensure%20accountability%20for%20those%20who%20exploit%20minors.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726987080000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-06%2Folj5u4a8_police-generic-image_625x300_18_June_24.jpg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fbhopal-news%2Fseries-of-child-sexual-abu