rl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia-indiatimes-com.cdn.ampproject.org%2Fc%2Fs%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-says-too-late-after-harris-accepts-another-debate-proposal%2Famp_articleshow%2F113563803.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fus%2Ftrump-says-too-late-after-harris-accepts-another-debate-proposal%2Famp_articleshow%2F113563803.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Security%20Council%20To%20Space%20Tech%3A%20Key%20Takeaways%20From%20Modi-Biden%20Meet%20In%20US%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EUS%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20commended%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20historic%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20amid%20the%20war%20with%20Russia.%20The%20US%20also%20backed%20permanent%20membership%20for%20India%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EHere%20Are%20Some%20Of%20The%20Key%20Takeaways%20From%20The%20Bilateral%20Meet%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Feach-time-we-sit-down-biden-posts-pics-of-meeting-pm-modi-6619870%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%20%26quot%3BEach%20Time%20We%20Sit%20Down...%26quot%3B%3A%20Biden%20Posts%20Pics%20Of%20Meeting%20PM%20Modi%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EBoost%20For%20India-US%20Ties%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20met%20the%20US%20president%20at%20his%20home%20in%20Wilmington%2C%20North%20Carolina.%20At%20the%20meeting%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20conveyed%20his%20appreciation%20for%20President%20Biden's%20unparalleled%20contributions%20in%20giving%20impetus%20to%20the%20India-US%20partnership%2C%20the%20Ministry%20of%20External%20Affairs%20said.%20Recalling%20his%20earlier%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20last%20year%20and%20President%20Biden's%20India%20trip%20for%20the%20G20%20summit%2C%20the%20Prime%20Minister%20noted%20that%20visits%20have%20led%20to%20greater%20dynamism%20and%20depth%20in%20the%20India-US%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20Prime%20Minister%20emphasised%20that%20India%20and%20the%20US%20now%20enjoy%20a%20comprehensive%20global%20strategic%20partnership%20that%20covers%20all%20areas%20of%20human%20endeavour%2C%20driven%20by%20shared%20democratic%20values%2C%20convergence%20of%20interests%20and%20vibrant%20people-to-people%20ties%2C%20the%20MEA%20said.%20It%20added%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20discussed%20ways%20to%20enhance%20bilateral%20cooperation%20in%20areas%20of%20mutual%20interest%20and%20exchanged%20views%20on%20global%20and%20regional%20issues%2C%20including%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region%20and%20beyond.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EIndia's%20Global%20Role%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20expressed%20appreciation%20for%20India's%20leadership%20on%20the%20world%20stage%2C%20particularly%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20leadership%20in%20the%20G20%20and%20the%20Global%20South%2C%20a%20White%20House%20statement%20said.%20The%20US%20President%20also%20praised%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20commitment%20to%20strengthen%20the%20Quad%20to%20ensure%20a%20free%2C%20open%2C%20and%20prosperous%20Indo-Pacific.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BIndia%20is%20at%20the%20forefront%20of%20efforts%20to%20seek%20solutions%20to%20the%20most%20pressing%20challenges%2C%20from%20supporting%20the%20global%20response%20to%20the%20COVID-19%20pandemic%20to%20addressing%20the%20devastating%20consequences%20of%20conflicts%20around%20the%20world%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%2C%20it%20said%2C%20commended%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20for%20his%20historic%20visits%20to%20Poland%20and%20Ukraine%2C%20the%20first%20by%20an%20Indian%20Prime%20Minister%20in%20decades%2C%20and%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20and%20ongoing%20humanitarian%20support%20for%20Ukraine.%20The%20statement%20was%20silent%20on%20the%20Prime%20Minister's%20visit%20to%20Russia.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20told%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20that%20the%20US%20supports%20initiatives%20to%20reform%20global%20institutions%20to%20%26quot%3Breflect%20India's%20important%20voice%26quot%3B.%20The%20US%20also%20backed%20permanent%20membership%20for%20India%20in%20a%20reformed%20UN%20Security%20Council.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3ESpace%20To%20Semiconductors%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20White%20House%20has%20said%20that%20the%20two%20leaders%20cheered%20the%20success%20of%20the%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technology%20(iCET)%20in%20deepening%20and%20expanding%20strategic%20cooperation%20across%20key%20technology%20sectors%2C%20including%20space%2C%20semiconductors%2C%20and%20advanced%20telecommunications.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BBoth%20Leaders%20committed%20to%20enhance%20regular%20engagements%20to%20improve%20the%20momentum%20of%20collaboration%20in%20fields%20such%20as%20artificial%20intelligence%2C%20quantum%2C%20biotechnology%2C%20and%20clean%20energy.%20They%20highlighted%20ongoing%20efforts%20to%20strengthen%20collaboration%20with%20like-minded%20partners%2C%20including%20through%20the%20Quad%20and%20a%20U.S.-India-ROK%20Trilateral%20Technology%20initiative%20launched%20earlier%20this%20year%20to%20build%20more%20secure%20and%20resilient%20supply%20chains%20for%20critical%20industries%20and%20ensure%20we%20collectively%20remain%20at%20the%20leading%20edge%20of%20innovation%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%20The%20leaders%2C%20it%20said%2C%20also%20endorsed%20new%20mechanisms%20for%20deeper%20cyberspace%20cooperation%20through%20the%20bilateral%20cybersecurity%20dialogue.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BPresident%20Biden%20and%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi%20hailed%20a%20watershed%20arrangement%20to%20establish%20a%20new%20semiconductor%20fabrication%20plant%20focused%20on%20advanced%20sensing%2C%20communication%2C%20and%20power%20electronics%20for%20national%20security%2C%20next%20generation%20telecommunications%2C%20and%20green%20energy%20applications%2C%26quot%