2C%20and%20overhaul%20(MRO)%20sector%2C%20including%20on%20all%20aircraft%20and%20aircraft%20engine%20parts%20thereby%20simplifying%20the%20tax%20structure%20and%20paving%20the%20way%20for%20building%20a%20strong%20ecosystem%20for%20MRO%20services%20in%20India.%20The%20Leaders%20also%20encouraged%20the%20industry%20to%20foster%20collaboration%20and%20drive%20innovation%20to%20support%20India's%20efforts%20to%20become%20a%20leading%20aviation%20hub%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20hailed%20the%20teaming%20agreement%20on%20the%20C-130J%20Super%20Hercules%20aircraft%20recently%20signed%20between%20Lockheed%20Martin%20and%20Tata%20Advanced%20Systems%20Limited%2C%20the%20two%20companies%20that%20co-chair%20the%20U.S.-India%20CEO%20Forum.%20Building%20on%20longstanding%20industry%20cooperation%2C%20this%20agreement%20will%20establish%20a%20new%20Maintenance%2C%20Repair%20and%20Overhaul%20(MRO)%20facility%20in%20India%20to%20support%20the%20readiness%20of%20the%20Indian%20fleet%20and%20global%20partners%20who%20operate%20the%20C-130%20Super%20Hercules%20aircraft%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said%2C%20adding%20that%20this%20marks%20a%20significant%20step%20in%20US-India%20cooperation%20in%20the%20defence%20and%20aerospace%20sector.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Findia-us-to-elevate-bilateral-ties-to-expand-clean-energy-supply-chains-6621420%5C%22%3EREAD%3A%20India%2C%20US%20To%20Elevate%20Bilateral%20Ties%20To%20Expand%20Clean%20Energy%20Supply%20Chains%3C%2Fa%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EClean%20Energy%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20and%20President%20Biden%20welcomed%20the%20joint%20efforts%20to%20accelerate%20the%20expansion%20of%20safe%20and%20secure%20clean%20energy%20supply%20chains%20through%20US%20and%20Indian%20manufacturing%20of%20clean%20energy%20technologies%20and%20components.%20%26quot%3BIn%20its%20initial%20phase%2C%20the%20U.S.%20and%20India%20would%20work%20together%20to%20unlock%20%241%20billion%20of%20multilateral%20financing%20to%20support%20projects%20across%20the%20clean%20energy%20value%20chain%20for%20renewable%20energy%2C%20energy%20storage%2C%20power%20grid%20and%20transmission%20technologies%2C%20high%20efficiency%20cooling%20systems%2C%20zero%20emission%20vehicles%2C%20and%20other%20emerging%20clean%20technologies%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20also%20highlighted%20the%20U.S.%20International%20Development%20Finance%20Corporation%20(DFC)'s%20partnership%20with%20India's%20private%20sector%20to%20expand%20clean%20energy%20manufacturing%20and%20diversify%20supply%20chains.%20To%20date%2C%20DFC%20has%20extended%20a%20%24250%20million%20loan%20to%20Tata%20Power%20Solar%20to%20construct%20a%20solar%20cell%20manufacturing%20facility%20and%20a%20%24500%20million%20loan%20to%20First%20Solar%20to%20construct%20and%20operate%20a%20solar%20module%20manufacturing%20facility%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20welcomed%20the%20India-US%20collaboration%20on%20a%20new%20National%20Center%20for%20Hydrogen%20Safety%20in%20India%20and%20affirmed%20their%20intent%20to%20utilise%20the%20new%20Renewable%20Energy%20Technology%20Action%20Platform%20(RETAP)%20to%20enhance%20collaboration%20on%20clean%20energy%20manufacturing%20and%20global%20supply%20chains.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20welcomed%20the%20progress%20made%20on%20joint%20efforts%20since%202023%20for%20India%20to%20work%20toward%20IEA%20membership%20in%20accordance%20with%20the%20provisions%20of%20the%20Agreement%20on%20an%20International%20Energy%20Program.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20Leaders%20reaffirmed%20their%20commitment%20to%20accelerating%20the%20manufacturing%20and%20deployment%20of%20renewable%20energy%2C%20battery%20storage%20and%20emerging%20clean%20technology%20in%20India%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%3Cstrong%3EPromoting%20Global%20Health%20and%20Development%3C%2Fstrong%3E%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20two%20leaders%20celebrated%20the%20new%20US-India%20Drug%20Policy%20Framework%2C%20which%20will%20deepen%20the%20collaboration%20to%20disrupt%20the%20illicit%20production%20and%20international%20trafficking%20of%20synthetic%20drugs%20and%20precursor%20chemicals%2C%20and%20deepen%20a%20holistic%20public%20health%20partnership.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20applauded%20the%20first-ever%20U.S.-India%20Cancer%20Dialogue%20held%20in%20August%202024%2C%20which%20brought%20together%20experts%20from%20both%20countries%20to%20increase%20research%20and%20development%20to%20accelerate%20the%20rate%20of%20progress%20against%20cancer%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20leaders%20welcomed%20the%20signing%20of%20Memorandum%20of%20Understanding%20(MoU)%20between%20the%20Ministry%20of%20Micro%2C%20Small%20and%20Medium%20Enterprises%20and%20Small%20Business%20Administration%20for%20promoting%20cooperation%20between%20U.S.%20and%20Indian%20small%20and%20medium-size%20enterprises%20by%20improving%20their%20participation%20in%20the%20global%20market%20place%20through%20capacity%20building%20workshops%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20trade%20and%20export%20finance%2C%20technology%20and%20digital%20trade%2C%20green%20economy%20and%20trade%20facilitation%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20welcomed%20enhanced%20cooperation%20on%20agriculture%20between%20the%20U.S.%20Department%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20India's%20Ministry%20of%20Agriculture%20and%20Farmers%20Welfare%2C%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20climate-smart%20agriculture%2C%20agriculture%20productivity%20growth%2C%20agriculture%20innovation%2C%20and%20sharing%20best%20practices%20related%20to%20crop%20risk%20protection%20and%20agriculture%20credit.%20The%20two%20sides%20will%20also%20enhance%20cooperation%20with%20the%20private%20sector%20through%20discussions%20on%20regulatory%20issues%20and%20innovation%20to%20enhance%20bilateral%20trade%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20White%20House%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726980180000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fc.ndtvimg.com%2F2024-09%2Fgp6g6l_modi-biden-afp_625x300_22_September_24.jpeg%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-joe-biden-quad-security-council-to-space-tech-key-takeaways-of-modi-biden-meet-in-us-6621683%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20commended%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20for%20his%20historic%20visit%20to%20Ukraine%20and%20his%20message%20of%20peace%20amid%20the%20war%20with%20Russia.%20The%20US%20also%20backed%20permanent%20membership%20for%20India%20in%20the%20UN%20Security%20Council.%22%2C%22author%22%3A%22%22%2C%22engagement%22%3A0%2C%22canonicalUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.ndtv.com%2Fworld-news%2Fpm-narendra-modi-joe-biden-quad-security-council-to-space-tech-key-takeaways-of-modi-biden-meet-in-us-6621683%22%2C%22cdnAmpUrl%22%3A%22%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22Has%20OTT%20reached%20a%20saturation%20point%3F%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%22%2C%22published%22%3A1726979400000%2C%22visual%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Fstatic.toiimg.com%2Fphoto%2Fmsid-113548322%2Cimgsize-206510.cms%22%2C%22originID%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fentertainment%2Fhindi%2Fbollywood%2Fnews%2Fthe-great-indian-content-crisis-as-theatrical-releases-slow-down-ott-reaches-a-saturation-point-where-is-the-middle-ground%2Farticleshow%2F113548389.cms%22%2C%22summary%22%3A%22%3Cimg%20border%3D%5C%220%5C%22%20align%3D%5C%22left%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fphoto%2F113548389.cms%5C%22%20hspace%3D%5C%2210%5C%22%3EThe%20Hindi%20film%20industry%20is%20experiencing%20a%20crisis%20due%20to%20fewer%20theatrical%20releases%20and%20OTT%20platform%20saturation.%20Dominated%20by%20major%20production%20houses%20and%20to