times.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-airstrike-on-gaza-school-claims-22-lives-military-cites-hamas-command-center%2Famp_articleshow%2F113563170.cms%22%2C%22ampUrl%22%3A%22https%3A%2F%2Ftimesofindia.indiatimes.com%2Fworld%2Fmiddle-east%2Fisraeli-airstrike-on-gaza-school-claims-22-lives-military-cites-hamas-command-center%2Famp_articleshow%2F113563170.cms%22%7D%2C%7B%22title%22%3A%22India%2C%20US%20To%20Elevate%20Bilateral%20Ties%20To%20Expand%20Clean%20Energy%20Supply%20Chains%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20India%20plan%20to%20elevate%20bilateral%20technical%2C%20financial%2C%20and%20policy%20support%20to%20expand%20complementary%20manufacturing%20capacity%20for%20building%20on%20existing%20clean%20energy%20cooperation%20between%20the%20two%20nations%2C%20according%20to%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20announcement%20on%20Saturday%20came%20after%20the%20meeting%20of%20Prime%20Minister%20Narendra%20Modi%20and%20US%20President%20Joe%20Biden%20at%20Greenville%2C%20Delaware.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20is%20in%20the%20US%20on%20a%20three-day%20visit.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ETo%20launch%20the%20partnership%20for%20establishing%20a%20%26quot%3Bshared%2C%20resilient%2C%20and%20cutting-edge%20techno-industrial%20base%26quot%3B%20centred%20on%20innovative%20clean%20energy%20manufacturing%20techniques%2C%20the%20US%20and%20India%20are%20%26quot%3Bworking%20to%20unlock%20USD%201%20billion%20in%20new%20multilateral%20finance%20through%20the%20International%20Bank%20for%20Reconstruction%20and%20Development%20(IBRD)%20for%20projects%2C%20including%20catalysing%20India's%20domestic%20clean%20energy%20supply%20chain%20buildout%26quot%3B%2C%20the%20White%20House%20said%20in%20a%20statement.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20partnership%20will%20look%20to%20expand%20complementary%20US%20and%20Indian%20manufacturing%20capacity%20for%20clean%20energy%20technologies%20and%20components%20and%20lay%20the%20groundwork%20for%20enhanced%20cooperation%20in%20third%20countries%2C%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20partnerships%20in%20Africa.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThis%20effort%20will%20build%20on%20existing%20clean%20energy%20cooperation%20between%20the%20US%20and%20India%2C%20including%20clean%20energy%20initiatives%20launched%20during%20Prime%20Minister%20Modi's%20visit%20to%20the%20US%20in%202023%2C%20and%20the%20Strategic%20Clean%20Energy%20Partnership%20led%20by%20the%20US%20Department%20of%20Energy%20and%20Government%20of%20India%20ministries%2C%20among%20other%20initiatives.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US-India%20partnership%20%26quot%3Bsets%20a%20strong%20example%20for%20the%20world%20and%20positions%20our%20countries%20to%20lead%20clean%20economic%20development%20in%20the%2021st%20century%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20statement%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20United%20States%20and%20India%20share%20an%20enduring%20commitment%20to%20deepen%20our%20collaboration%20on%20issues%20of%20shared%20national%20and%20economic%20security.%20As%20an%20important%20aspect%20of%20our%20economic%20growth%20agendas%2C%20we%20are%20committed%20to%20working%20together%20to%20capture%20the%20benefits%20of%20the%20clean%20energy%20transition%2C%20including%20the%20creation%20of%20high-quality%20jobs%20for%20our%20populations%2C%20acceleration%20of%20clean%20energy%20deployment%20globally%2C%20and%20achievement%20of%20global%20climate%20goals%2C%26quot%3B%20it%20said.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BOver%20time%2C%20we%20seek%20to%20mobilise%20additional%20financing%20into%20priority%20clean%20energy%20manufacturing%20sectors%20that%20harness%20public%20and%20private%20financial%20tools%20and%20pioneer%20innovative%20financial%20vehicles%20to%20meet%20the%20rapid%20demand%20for%20flexible%20climate%20finance%20solutions%2C%26quot%3B%20said%20the%20White%20House.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3ENoting%20that%20the%20United%20States%20and%20India%20intend%20to%20work%20with%20relevant%20government%20agencies%2C%20civil%20society%20and%20the%20private%