ince%20the%20conflict%20began%20in%20early%20October.%20The%20Israel%20Defense%20Forces%20(IDF)%20intercepted%20most%20of%20the%20missiles%2C%20but%20one%20man%20in%20his%2060s%20suffered%20minor%20injuries%20from%20shrapnel.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EHezbollah%20claimed%20responsibility%20for%20the%20missile%20barrage%20and%20stated%20that%20it%20had%20aimed%20at%20the%20Ramat%20David%20Airbase.%20Located%2050%20km%20from%20the%20Lebanon%20border%2C%20the%20airbase%20is%20a%20key%20strategic%20site%20for%20the%20Israeli%20Air%20Force.%C2%A0%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20response%2C%20Israeli%20jets%20carried%20out%20a%20series%20of%20retaliatory%20strikes%20across%20southern%20Lebanon.%20The%20IDF%20reported%20that%20its%20airstrikes%20targeted%20at%20least%20110%20Hezbollah%20positions%2C%20including%20rocket%20launchers%20and%20operational%20facilities.%20The%20IDF%20claims%20it%20successfully%20disrupted%20Hezbollah's%20preparations%20for%20further%20rocket%20launches.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20IDF%20stated%20that%20their%20Saturday%20afternoon%20air%20raids%20hit%20approximately%20290%20Hezbollah%20sites%2C%20including%20thousands%20of%20rocket%20launcher%20barrels%2C%20as%20part%20of%20their%20strategy%20to%20dismantle%20Hezbollah's%20rocket-firing%20capabilities.%20These%20preemptive%20strikes%20were%20launched%20to%20degrade%20Hezbollah's%20ability%20to%20launch%20large-scale%20attacks%20on%20Israeli%20territory.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EThe%20intensification%20of%20Israeli%20airstrikes%20follows%20Hezbollah's%20earlier%20attack%20on%20Israeli%20military%20targets%2C%20including%20seven%20positions%20in%20northern%20Israel%20and%20the%20Golan%20Heights.%20Israel's%20military%20reported%20that%20Hezbollah%20had%20fired%20about%2090%20rockets%20at%20Israeli%20forces%20during%20these%20engagements.%3C%2Fli%3E%5Cn%3Cli%3EIn%20addition%20to%20military%20targets%2C%20Israel%20conducted%20an%20airstrike%20on%20southern%20Beirut%2C%20killing%20senior%20Hezbollah%20commander