nent%20categories%20of%20membership.%20%3Ca%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.whitehouse.gov%2Fbriefing-room%2Fstatements-releases%2F2024%2F09%2F21%2Fjoint-fact-sheet-the-united-states-and-india-continue-to-expand-comprehensive-and-global-strategic-partnership%2F%5C%22%3EIn%20a%20joint%20statement%3C%2Fa%3E%2C%20the%20leaders%20said%20that%20the%20India-US%20partnership%20%26quot%3Bis%20vital%20to%20the%20success%20of%20efforts%20to%20build%20a%20cleaner%2C%20inclusive%2C%20more%20secure%2C%20and%20more%20prosperous%20future%20for%20the%20planet.%26quot%3B%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPresident%20Biden%20commended%20India's%20leadership%2C%20particularly%20PM%20Modi's%20role%20in%20the%20G-20%20and%20the%20Global%20South%20and%20acknowledged%20the%20PM's%20recent%20visits%20to%20Poland%20and%20Ukraine.%20The%20discussion%20around%20India's%20potential%20inclusion%20as%20a%20permanent%20member%20of%20the%20UNSC%20is%20part%20of%20a%20larger%20conversation%20about%20reforming%20global%20institutions%20to%20reflect%20current%20geopolitical%20realities.%20India%2C%20with%20its%20large%20population%2C%20expanding%20economy%2C%20and%20active%20role%20in%20international%20peacekeeping%20and%20diplomacy%2C%20has%20long%20advocated%20for%20such%20reforms.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%26quot%3BThe%20Leaders%20reaffirmed%20their%20support%20for%20the%20freedom%20of%20navigation%20and%20the%20protection%20of%20commerce%2C%20including%20critical%20maritime%20routes%20in%20the%20Middle%20East%20where%20India%20will%20assume%20co-lead%20in%202025%20of%20the%20Combined%20Task%20Force%20150%20to%20work%20with%20Combined%20Maritime%20Forces%20to%20secure%20sea%20lanes%20in%20the%20Arabian%20Sea%2C%26quot%3B%20the%20joint%20statement%20added.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EDuring%20the%20Quad%20summit%2C%20PM%20Modi%20reiterated%20the%20importance%20of%20a%20%26quot%3Bfree%2C%20open%2C%20inclusive%2C%20and%20prosperous%20Indo-Pacific.%26quot%3B%20PM%20Modi%20highlighted%20several%20initiatives%2C%20including%20collaborations%20in%20health%20security%2C%20emerging%20technologies%2C%20and%20climate%20change%2C%20aimed%20at%20addressing%20global%20challenges.%20He%20described%20the%20Quad%20as%20a%20%26quot%3Bforce%20for%20global%20good%2C%26quot%3B%20committed%20to%20fostering%20cooperation%20for%20the%20benefit%20of%20all.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20India%20are%20working%20together%20to%20expand%20clean%20energy%20manufacturing%20and%20strengthen%20their%20technological%20and%20industrial%20bases.%20The%20Biden%20administration%20has%20announced%20plans%20to%20unlock%20%241%20billion%20in%20new%20multilateral%20financing%20through%20the%20International%20Bank%20for%20Reconstruction%20and%20Development%20(IBRD)%20for%20clean%20energy%20projects%20in%20India.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EPrime%20Minister%20Modi%20announced%20a%20%247.5%20million%20grant%20for%20cancer%20testing%2C%20screening%2C%20and%20diagnostics%20in%20the%20Indo-Pacific%20region.%20The%20grant%20forms%20part%20of%20India's%20broader%20'One%20Earth%2C%20One%20Health'%20vision%2C%20which%20seeks%20to%20share%20India's%20expertise%20in%20healthcare%20and%20provide%20assistance%20in%20areas%20such%20as%20radiotherapy%20and%20capacity%20building.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20US%20and%20India%20also%20announced%20advancements%20in%20technology%20and%20defence%20cooperation.%20The%20Initiative%20on%20Critical%20and%20Emerging%20Technology%20(iCET)%20continues%20to%20strengthen%20strategic%20ties%20between%20the%20two%20nations%20in%20key%20technology%20sectors%2C%20including%20semiconductors.%20A%20new%20semiconductor%20fabrication%20plant%20will%20be%20established%2C%20supported%20by%20India's%20Semiconductor%20Mission%20and%20a%20partnership%20with%20US%20companies%20like%20Bharat%20Semi%20and%203rdiTech.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%20defence%2C%20the%20two%20countries%20have%20deepened%20industrial%20cooperation%2C%20with%20projects%20such%20as%20the%20co-development%20of%20unmanned%20surface%20vehi