n%20its%20first%20batch%20of%20100%20MBBS%20students%20for%20its%20inaugural%20academic%20session%202023-24.%20The%20youth%20of%20the%20Northeastern%20state%20saw%20this%20decision%20as%20a%20lifeline%20to%20their%20dreams.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EOne%20of%20the%20brightest%20minds%20of%20his%20batch%2C%20Zavi%20recalls%20the%20monumental%20decision%2C%20saying%2C%20%E2%80%9CI%20felt%20relieved.%20The%20other%20option%20would%20be%20to%20move%20to%20Assam%20or%20Shillong%20to%20attend%20the%20medical%20college%20there.%20Studying%20in%20the%20same%20state%20where%20I%20was%20born%20makes%20me%20feel%20fortunate%3B%20I%20feel%20lucky%20to%20be%20among%20the%20first%20batch%20of%20medical%20students.%20The%20fact%20that%20I%20live%2030%20minutes%20away%20from%20college%20feels%20amazing.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1725974773.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20batch%20of%20medical%20students%20at%20the%20Nagaland%20Institute%20of%20Medical%20Sciences%20and%20Research%20(NIMSR)%20in%20Kohima%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1725974773.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1725974773-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1725974773-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1725974773-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-1725974773-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365387%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22w