ans%20Kohima%20is%20not%20the%20first%20choice%20of%20those%20who%20are%20looking%20for%20a%20job%20change.%20But%20Dr%20Soumya%20stands%20proud%20of%20the%20team%20of%20500%20staff%20who%20are%20spread%20across%20the%20hospital%20and%20medical%20college.%20Not%20to%20forget%20her%20%E2%80%9Cdream%20team%20of%20three%E2%80%9D%20%E2%80%94%20Lilly%20Ezung%2C%20technical%20consultant%3B%20Tali%20Jamir%2C%20procurement%20consultant%20and%20A%20Solo%2C%20hospital%20administrator%20%E2%80%94%20who%2C%20she%20says%2C%20have%20been%20working%20day%20and%20night%20since%202022%20to%20see%20the%20project%20to%20fruition.%20%E2%80%9CIf%20I%20lose%20one%20of%20them%2C%20then%20the%20college%20may%20collapse.%20They%20are%20the%20heart%20of%20the%20college%2C%E2%80%9D%20she%20points%20out.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cdiv%20class%3D%5C%22wp-block-image%5C%22%3E%5Cn%3Cfigure%3E%3Cimg%20sizes%3D%5C%22(max-width%3A%201200px)%20100vw%2C%201200px%5C%22%20src%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-4-1725975238.jpg%5C%22%20width%3D%5C%221200%5C%22%20alt%3D%5C%22The%20college%20is%20equipped%20with%2030%20laboratories%2C%20staff%20quarters%2C%20a%20sports%20complex%2C%20lecture%20theatres%2C%20and%20a%20330-bed%20hospital.%5C%22%20srcset%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-4-1725975238.jpg%201200w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-4-1725975238-300x157.jpg%20300w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-4-1725975238-500x262.jpg%20500w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-4-1725975238-768x402.jpg%20768w%2C%20https%3A%2F%2Fen-media.thebetterindia.com%2Fuploads%2F2024%2F09%2Fnagaland-medical-college-4-1725975238-150x79.jpg%20150w%5C%22%20class%3D%5C%22wp-image-365401%5C%22%20height%3D%5C%22628%5C%22%3E%3Cfigcaption%20class%3D%5C%22wp-element-caption%5C%22%3EThe%20college%20is%20equipped%20with%2030%20laboratories%2C%20staff%20quarters%2C%20a%20sports%20complex%2C%20lecture%20theatres%2C%20and%20a%20330-bed%20hospital.%3C%2Ffigcaption%3E%3C%2Ffigure%3E%3C%2Fdiv%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EThe%20curriculum%20is%20designed%20in%20line%20with%20the%20National%20Medical%20Commission%20standards%20with%20subjects%20such%20as%20anatomy%2C%20gynaecology%2C%20and%20surgery%20along%20with%20a%20focus%20on%20clinical%20exposure.%20%E2%80%9CWe%20also%20follow%20the%20Medical%20Council%20of%20India%E2%80%99s%20AETCOM%20(attitude%2C%20ethics%20and%20communication%20module).%20This%20is%20a%20community-oriented%20curriculum%20with%20family%20adoption%20programmes%20in%20rural%20setups%20of%20the%20state%20to%20ensure%20that%20no%20one%20in%20society%20is%20left%20out.%E2%80%9D%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWith%20over%2030%20laboratories%20%E2%80%94%20for%20micro-anatomy%2C%20histopathology%2C%20bacteriology%2C%20etc%20%E2%80%94%20the%20college%20is%20equipped%20with%20everything%20a%20medical%20student%20would%20need.%20On%20most%20days%2C%20Zavi%20can%20be%20found%20in%20the%20anatomy%20lab%2C%20brushing%20up%20on%20the%20names%20of%20the%20different%20bones.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3E%E2%80%9CMy%20experience%20at%20the%20college%20has%20been%20really%20great%20so%20far.%20I%20learn%20so%20much%20and%20am%20given%20so%20many%20opportunities.%20The%20facilities%20have%20helped%20me%20understand%20concepts%20better.%20I%20know%20of%20youth%20who%20are%20working%20hard%20day%20and%20night%20to%20get%20into%20this%20college%2C%20and%20it%20is%20a%20step%20towards%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F351914%2Forgan-donation-in-india-donor-mohan-foundation-dr-sunil-shroff-kbc-episode-kidney-transplant%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eencouraging%20the%20future%20doctors%20%3C%2Fa%3Eof%20Nagaland%2C%E2%80%9D%20he%20smiles%2C%20going%20back%20to%20the%2