ndoned%20People%22%2C%22content%22%3A%22%3Cp%3EA%20blind%20eye%2C%20a%20deaf%20ear%20%E2%80%94%20this%20is%20what%20the%20vulnerable%20in%20today%E2%80%99s%20world%20are%20subjected%20to%20when%20they%20call%20out%20for%20help.%20But%20Gurugram%E2%80%99s%20Jas%20Kalra%20is%20making%20sure%20they%20are%20seen%2C%20heard%2C%20and%20served.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EJas%E2%80%99%20journey%20of%20selfless%20service%20to%20people%2C%20or%20%3Cem%3Esewa%3C%2Fem%3E%20as%20he%20words%20it%2C%20did%20not%20have%20a%20defined%20starting%20point.%20Since%20he%20was%20only%20nine%20years%20old%2C%20he%20had%20seen%20his%20father%20Ravi%20Kalra%20devote%20all%20his%20energy%20to%20helping%20society%2C%20whether%20it%20was%20for%20the%20community%2C%20animals%2C%20or%20the%20environment.%C2%A0%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EIn%202008%2C%20Ravi%20founded%20the%20Earth%20Saviours%20Foundation%20and%20would%20personally%20go%20out%20into%20the%20streets%20to%20find%20disabled%20and%20destitute%20people%20%E2%80%94%20bringing%20them%20into%20the%20foundation%E2%80%99s%20shelter%20home%2C%20and%20%3Ca%20rel%3D%5C%22noreferrer%20noopener%5C%22%20href%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fthebetterindia.com%2F358496%2Fyojana-gharat-smit-old-age-home-care-foundation-social-worker-abandoned-elders-thane-mumbai-maharashtra-donate%2F%5C%22%20target%3D%5C%22_blank%5C%22%3Eserving%20them%20around%20the%20clock%3C%2Fa%3E.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cp%3EWhen%20Jas%20turned%2021%2C%20he%20had%20already%20started%20learning%20from%20his%20father%20and%20hoped%20to%20continue%20his%20legacy.%20However%2C%20fate%20had%20other%20plans.%20After%20just%20four%20short%20months%20of%20learning%20from%20his%20father%2C%20Jas%20lost%20him.%20He%20was%20left%20to%20carry%20on%20his%20work%20in%20what%20would%20become%20the%20toughest%20journey%20of%20his%20life.%3C%2Fp%3E%5Cn%3Cblockquote%20data-instgrm-version%3D%5C%2214%5C%22%20data-instgrm-permalink%3D%5C%22https%3A%2F%2Fwww.instagram.com%2Freel%2FC_VGawSSgry%2F%3Futm_source%3Dig_embed%26am